These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, coral, black, emerald, aquamarine, grey, azure
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, western, horror, satire, action, martial-arts, spy
 1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who likes black##1
11. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Color           | aquamarine | emerald | coral | black | pink | grey | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | action   | satire      | martial-arts | horror    | western    | spy         |

