.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, family, horror, disaster, adventure, drama, scientific
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, skateboarding, golf, ice-hockey, rowing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre          | epic | family | adventure | disaster | drama | scientific | horror |
| Sport   | soccer      | skateboarding   | golf   | ice-hockey      | badminton       | surfing       | rowing     |

