.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
City: colone, venice, hamburg, nizza, new-york, san-francisco, marseilles
There are 7 different nationalities: german, italian, australian, egyptian, canadian, british, mexican
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the mexican##1
 3. the italian is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 5. the german is the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the australian is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the australian##1
 8. the italian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the egyptian##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the german##1
11. the egyptian is in the middle##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| City   | venice | new-york     | hamburg  | san-francisco       | colone       | marseilles  | nizza   |
| Nationality    | british  | german | mexican | egyptian | italian | australian | canadian |

