.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
City: hannover, marseilles, nizza, venice, berlin, boston, colone
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, bongani, fonseca, dannemann, ritmeester, cain
 1. the person traveling to berlin is the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the cain-smoker is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| City   | boston    | colone     | venice     | nizza      | marseilles | berlin      | hannover     |
| Cigar   | fonseca | bongani | ritmeester | dannemann | cain | oliveros | bluemaster |

