.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, orchid, poppy, lily, azalea, daisy
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, december, march, october, may, april, november
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | orchid | azalea     | poppy | daisy | lily | sunflower |
| Birthday     | november   | march    | may | april     | august         | october     | december        |

