.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, dancer, coach, videographer, police-officer, project-manager
7 different games are played: snooker, domino, poker, canasta, backgammon, monopoly, whist
 1. the police-officer is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 2. the coach is on the left of the videographer##1
 3. the project-manager is the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 5. the police-officer is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person playing snooker is the dancer##1
 8. the videographer is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the project-manager##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Job   | freelancer  | project-manager | coach | videographer | police-officer     | entrepreneur | dancer |
| Game     | monopoly | canasta      | whist | poker    | backgammon | domino   | snooker  |

