.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, chinchilla, dog, rat, pony, ferret
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, accountant, nurse, pilot, analyst, writer, coach
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the pilot##1
 2. the coach is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the snake is the nurse##1
 4. the nurse is on the far left##1
 5. the analyst is on the right of the pilot##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is the pilot##1
 7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet       | snake   | dog | ferret | pony | rabbit     | chinchilla | rat |
| Job   | nurse | writer      | firefighter        | coach         | accountant | pilot     | analyst |

