 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of country##1
 6. the prince-smoker is the fan of pop##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 9. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
11. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
