.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-10::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, baking, filmmaking, board-games, card-games, woodworking
House: craftsman, cottage, gothic-revival, modern, art-deco, futuristic, colonial
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the cottage house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the cottage house is on the right of the modern house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the art-deco house##1
10. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Hobby   | board-games    | baking    | gardening   | card-games | magic-tricks | woodworking | filmmaking   |
| House    | gothic-revival | art-deco | colonial | futuristic  | craftsman       | modern     | cottage |

