.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-14::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, ferret, fish, dog, guinea-pig, hamster
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, 7up, mirinda, cola, sprite, lemonade
 1. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking cola##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |      4       |  5   |     6     |     7      |
| Pet   | dog | ferret | hamster   | fish | snake | mouse | guinea-pig        |
| Beverage     | sprite | mirinda | 7up | coffee         | juice  | lemonade    | cola |

