 3. the person playing poker is the person who likes orange##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person playing chess##1
11. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7       |
| Game    | backgammon | chess | scrabble     | billiard | snooker | poker | monopoly       |
