.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-20::.
There 7 different types of food: onion, peach, strawberry, corn, cherry, cranberry, artichoke
City: marseilles, hannover, paris, miami, san-francisco, venice, rome
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person eating artichoke is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
11. the person eating peach is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |     5     |     6      |   7    |
| Food   | corn | cranberry | artichoke  | strawberry | onion | peach | cherry |
| City           | venice   | hannover    | san-francisco | miami      | paris      | marseilles | rome   |

 